---
// privacy.astro
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout>
    <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div>
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Last updated: 7/16/2026</p>
        </div>

        <section class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">The short version</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                You upload your own Instagram data export to analyze it. We process it to generate your results, then
                it's gone. We don't create an account for you, and we don't keep a copy of your export or your
                Instagram data on our servers after your request finishes.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">What we collect</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                When you upload your Instagram data export, we temporarily process it on our server to generate the
                analysis shown to you (such as follower/following comparisons and profile information). This
                processing happens in memory and in a temporary, isolated location that is automatically and
                permanently deleted immediately after your request completes. We do not write your export, or any
                data extracted from it, to a permanent database.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                We do not require an account, login, email address, or any other personal information to use this
                tool.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">What we don't do</h2>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 list-disc list-inside flex flex-col gap-1">
                <li>We don't sell, rent, or share your data with third parties.</li>
                <li>We don't use your data for advertising, and we don't run ad trackers on this site.</li>
                <li>We don't retain your Instagram export, or any data derived from it, after your session ends.</li>
                <li>We don't require you to create an account.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Anonymous usage counter</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                We keep a simple count of how many times this tool has been used, so we can track its usage. This
                counter does not store any information about you or the content of your upload; it's just a number
                that increments.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Children's privacy</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                This tool is not directed at children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect information from
                children under 13.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Your rights</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                Because we don't retain your data after processing, there is generally nothing stored for us to
                provide, correct, or delete on request. If you have questions about how your data was handled during
                a specific session, or any other privacy questions, you can reach out at [YOUR EMAIL].
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Changes to this policy</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                If this policy changes, for example, if we introduce optional accounts or persistent storage in the
                future: we'll update this page and change the "last updated" date above.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h2 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Contact</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                Questions? Reach out at [YOUR EMAIL], or open an issue on&nbsp;
                <a
                    href="https://github.com/tanmaykundapur/ig-sleuth"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="text-blue-600 hover:underline"
                >GitHub</a>.
            </p>
        </section>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>